@startuml
title Hình 4.3 - Context Map 13 Bounded Context

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #475569
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #475569
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #DCFCE7

left to right direction

component "Identity\nidentity-service\nKeycloak users" as Identity #DBEAFE
component "User Profile\nuser-service\nuser_db" as User #DBEAFE
component "Product Catalog\nproduct-service\nproduct_db + Redis" as Product #DCFCE7
component "Inventory\ninventory-service\ninventory_db" as Inventory #DCFCE7
component "Cart\ncart-service\nRedis cart keys" as Cart #DCFCE7
component "Order\norder-service\norder_db + Outbox\nSaga orchestrator" as Order #FEF3C7
component "Payment\npayment-service\npayment_db + Outbox\nVNPAY" as Payment #FEF3C7
component "Voucher\nvoucher-service\nvoucher_db" as Voucher #FEF3C7
component "Notification\nnotification-service\nnotification_db" as Notification #FCE7F3
component "Review\nreview-service\nreview_db" as Review #E0F2FE
component "Search\nsearch-service\nElasticsearch" as Search #E0F2FE
component "Content\ncontent-service\ncontent_db" as Content #F8FAFC
component "Flash Sale\nflash-sale-service\nflash_sale_db + Redis" as FlashSale #FEE2E2

Identity --> User : user-registered event
Product --> Search : product-created / updated / deleted
Cart --> Product : verify product\nREST/Feign
Order --> Product : price / status\nREST/Feign
Order --> Inventory : check stock\nREST/Feign + events
Order --> Voucher : validate / reserve voucher\nREST/Feign
Review --> Order : verify purchased product\nREST/Feign
Order --> Payment : payment-requested event\nor create VNPAY payment
Payment --> Order : payment-success / failed
Order --> Notification : order-confirmed / cancelled
Order --> Inventory : order-confirmed / cancelled
Order --> Voucher : order-cancelled\nrelease voucher
FlashSale --> Order : flash-sale-order-requested
FlashSale --> Redis : stock / buyers keys
Product --> Redis : product cache

note bottom
  Mỗi bounded context sở hữu dữ liệu và logic riêng.
  Quan hệ giữa context đi qua API công khai hoặc domain event Kafka.
end note

@enduml
